Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're going to talk about what is\Ninner peace and how does one achieve it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in uh and live with it in their\Nlifetime. So when I hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,um inner peace\Num I think of my um inner spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,uh body that is um always with me. Um,\Nis that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,correct that the inner peace is\Nsomething that you always carry with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you?\N>> Well, that that's your your definition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of it.\N>> Everybody has their own definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> Of what they would mean by spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,peace.\N>> Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You know, how closely they fulfill their\Ntheir own uh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,um ambitions about it.\NTo me, uh, inner peace is, uh, the the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptance of what is from instant to\Ninstant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with, uh, so if the bird is singing as\Nyou walk through the woods, you're happy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the bird is singing. If the bird is not\Nsinging, you're quiet. You're happy the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,bird is not singing because you can hear\Nevery little twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,uh so to be happy with the experience of\Nlife as you experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm experiencing it right now.\NIf I accept that I have some wonderment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of where we're going to go next with\Nconversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that's a normal experience to\Nwonder what is the next question going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to be.\NSo I accept that I have some mild not
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,apprehension but wonder. Yeah. Yeah. A\Nlittle apprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What will the next question be? And will\NI be able to adequately fulfill my own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,inner definition of adequacy of\Nexplanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm.\N>> Will I live up to my own inner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,expectations?\NSo the only fulfillment I have to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,about then is whether I'm fulfilling my\Nown inner expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness of presence of God is just\None of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, but it's more inclusive than\Njust that. There's also our
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,physical performance as human beings and\Nour intellectual performance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and our emotional compatibility\Nand our
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to ser serve some practical\Nuh purpose for the people who will be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing this uh this film as we as we\Nfinish it. Mhm. that I can stimulate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,them to ask themselves what to me is\Ninner peace? What to me is the full
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning of life?\NWhat part does the awareness of God play
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own inner experience and\Nexpectation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And you may have no uh understanding of\NGod or or even
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,uh wondering about it,\Nwhich is fine too because if it was up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to God for you to think about God now,\Nyou'd be thinking about God now. So if
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not, it's probably because\Ndoesn't God God doesn't want you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about God now.\NThe way to make God happy is don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,about God when God doesn't want you\Nthinking about God. How does that grab
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you\Nif you're thinking about it? It must be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the expectation unconsciously\Nto include God in one's definition of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfillment of happiness\Nand uh but not to be uh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,consciously aware of it from moment to\Nmoment because that stirs up an inner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,expectation. Mhm.\N>> You know, we all have an idea of God has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,having something to do with piety.\NPiety. So people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> you mentioned God, they expect the\Nexpectation of piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And um but the presence of God is more\Nthan just piety. P one B of one mode of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of it.\Num and going beyond piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The spontaneity of how this very moment\Nis unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,just this moment right now that I'm\Nspeaking of is unfolding of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,inner\Npotentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to become the reality of our experience.\NWhether we experience that reality or
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,not is irrelevant to the presence of\Nthat reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So my acceptance of the the presence of\NGod at this very moment is so complete
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and total that I don't have to think\Nabout it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that if God wants me to serve wants us\Nto serve others through our
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,communication\Nthrough what we're doing this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,then I feel we've uh fulfilled our uh\Npotentiality as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,my gift to other human beings is to\Nexpress myself to the fullest capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can of my own realization of the\Npresence of God as I have experienced it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout life\Nand in at different periods of life that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,experience has been quite different.\NSometimes it was overpoweringly present
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,other times I was oblivious of it\Nconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was too busy laughing and\Nhaving a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So at that time God was present as the\Nexperience of the joy of the moment of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,being an adult human being.\NWhen I was younger it was the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of God as the experience\Nof being a child, a happy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I'm very very happy right this\Nmoment with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,uh this moment I have no further\Nexpectation other than we are being who
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we are with each other at this moment\Nand and I love you very much and I want
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you to know the degree to which I love\Nyou
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and that fulfills uh\Num
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,some inner need on my part that I should\Nnot only feel what I feel about you but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,share with you how I feel about you.\NUh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the thankfulness\Nuh so I'm very thankful for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and your presence\Nbecause with your love and your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I become\Nu the greater fulfillment of my inner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,divine potential.\Nthat you help me fulfill the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the conscious awareness of the\Npresence of God within me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as existence because out of the\Nexistence of of being with you comes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that joy and the joy tells me that God\Nis here now present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I experience God as the happiness\Nthat I feel when I'm with you and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,chatting away with you. And at the same\Ntime, the back of my mind is saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"You could be doing it better." But\Nthat's BS. If I could be doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,better, I would. I would be.\NWell, when when I experience
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> inner peace, it's like a it's like a\Ncalm I think of it as a being a calm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,presence that is always within my aura,\N>> but sometimes, you know, the worldly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> things take over. And so it's always
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there, but there's\Ndaily activities and tasks that have to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,be accomplished.\N>> Distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So there's Yeah. So, but it's always\Nthere. Inner peace is always there. And
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know it's there.\N>> You know, um you get a kind of a inner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,peace when you do a job well done. You\Nknow that God helped you do that. um you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,get an inner peace when um you know you\Nsee a a child being born because you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,know that without God that would not\Nhave happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So I just feel like um inner peace is\Nsomething that's always within your
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,aura. It's just that you have to take\Nthe time to recognize it that a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,people you know because of the daily\Nactivities and things you know even just
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,planting a tree there's a certain piece\Nof
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,>> times in my life when I lost the inner\Npeace u the suffering of other I lose my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,inner peace when I witnessed the\Nsuffering of others the suffering of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,other beings humans or animals\Nuh bird u the witnessing a suffering I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,lose I lose that feeling of inner peace.\N>> Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh I don't know how to overcome that.\NU
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to witness the suffering of others.\N>> Well, if that's more of the compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that's in you that that takes over the\Ninner peace is always there though. But
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that wouldn't that be the\Ncompassion to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, peace is more the achievement of\Nthe goal. you know as a physician one of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I became a physician is uh to\Nrelieve the suffering of others
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh so to to witness the ongoingness\Nof suffering in someone else brings in a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering within me which can I can only\Neliminate by relieving their suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way I guess if you define it oddly\Nenough it's always selfish then to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,relieve the suffering of others because\Nthen I feel better that they're feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,better.\N>> But also it's also kind of fulfilling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because you know that you use the go the\Ngifts that God gave you to help that
