Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> is uh how to relieve the suffering of\Nothers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,uh by their you know whatever that\Nsuffering might be could be guilt it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,could be physical pain could be fear of\Nthe future it could be regret over the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,past\N>> it could be wor over their pets and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,animals you say I worry too much about\Nthe dog I will stop worrying about the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,dog instead I'll worry about the bird\Nwe got a talking parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who chatters away. Yes, she does.\N>> Oh, it's hysterically funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the meantime, I like all my\Nanimals. So, there's the doggy sitting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Then there's the kitty sitting\Nthere. And then there's the birdie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,chirping and talking away. And there's\Nyou and I talking about the birds and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the cats and the dogs all at the same\Ntime. So, it's sort of ciruitous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Their happiness makes us happy. And\Nbecause we're happy, they become happy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're happy.\N>> Right? That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> As the\Npresence of God is really the uh
