Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So our happiness and our gladness at the\Npresence of all the things we love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,uh is an expression of the fulfillment\Nof God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, if you had to describe\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What would you inner peace in yourself?\NIf you had to describe inner peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,could you give me a time that you really\Nfeel inner peace uh within yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What at what times do you feel that\Nstrong inner peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> When I'm fulfilling my potential to the\Nbest of my capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,like right now, I feel peaceful that I\Nam expressing myself as well as I can
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,under these circumstances.\Nthis couch, this camera, this time, this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature, this room.\NHypothetically, I might be more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,eloquent. But in reality, I'm being as\Neloquent as I can be right at this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,moment. And the love I feel from you\Ntends to charge it up. And then when we
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,took a break, we went in and checked out\Nall the the all the animals were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody's hunky dory. Everybody's\Nhappy. And
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so the fulfillment of that potential\Nuh brings brings a state of joy. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And and uh and I'm I'm happy that you're\Nsitting next to me and we're discussing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,such a subject.\NUm, would you consider inner peace an
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,emotional\Nstate or is it more of a physical
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,state?\N>> I I I understand as a state of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.\N>> Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> The entire state of consciousness which\Nincludes the emotion and the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,expectation.\NAnd what I just said, I've already
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered. I just remembered that I've\Nalready just said what I just said. So
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the immediate past. So there's the\Nimmediate past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to be said in the next\Nmoment? There's the immediate past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the immediate future. There's\Nthe immediate present. Uh all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,simultaneously. Past, present, and\Nfuture become melded into one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,overall experience.\Nmelt melted into one overall experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's not it's not an emotional it's and\Nit's not physical. So it's just
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> state.\N>> No, it's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's all of them.\N>> Yeah. You can't say it's not that. It's
