Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,>> that our facial expressions are\Nappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> It is a little bit on the darker side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is it? Yeah.\N>> Okay.
