Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um peace is\N>> all it feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. Um peace is it fulfilling um\Ninterex expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have uh like a inter do we\Nrecognize when we really feel uh inner
