Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I think we experience it without\Nactually defining it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,uh when asked to define it, I think it's\Neasy enough to define
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,except that it's difficult.\N>> Okay.
