Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.39,0:34:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You can\N>> once you're aware that it's there. Like
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.87,0:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,right now as I'm speaking to you, I'm\Naware the cameras are grinding, that
