Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.67,0:34:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the surface that disturbs the piece.\N>> Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.48,0:34:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,>> On the other hand, within myself\Nis the reality that all of that is
