Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.24,0:34:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of the moment. Okay? Whether\Nit's achieved or not is irre you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.24,0:34:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not irrelevant but secondary.\N>> So you talk about riding the quest the
