Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.56,0:35:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's a way of being you know so it's not\Na state from which you go from one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.35,0:35:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to another.\NYeah. Uh to me it's an overall intention
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.20,0:35:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> that colors everything\Nthat I'll be as real as I can be about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.07,0:35:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality as I experience it from\Nmoment to moment. So when we were in
