Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.96,0:35:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm.\N>> If we die, we die. And if we don't, we
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.00,0:35:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,don't. And uh\Nso there we are facing sudden death and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.48,0:35:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,at a state of profound peace at the very\Nmoment that they're facing the
