Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I was very peaceful with you. It was\Nlike our spirits were
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.80,0:36:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,became one.\N>> And I suppose during such states the
