Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.56,0:37:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. Whether you live or die was\Nirrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.59,0:37:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> So the experience of reality transcended
