Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.44,0:37:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our experience of the reality of the\Npresent moment was overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.59,0:37:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So we were basically riding the crest of\Nthat wave. That's where we were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.00,0:37:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> where we were. Uh because we weren't\Nconcerned with this or that. We were
