Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\NSo does permanent um how does one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.20,0:38:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,uh\Nuh bring to life uh in them the the how
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.16,0:38:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,does one\Num
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,live in permanent inner peace at all\Ntimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.16,0:38:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Just bringing up the question already\Nstarts it going.
