Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.00,0:39:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,regretful or fearful. Mhm.\N>> And they never knew what inner peace
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.00,0:39:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,was. Therefore, tranquilizers did serve\Na certain purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that because they began to experience\Nwhat it is to feel peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So tranquilizers I think u\Npharmacolog you know ph pharmacologic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.24,0:39:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,tranquilizers\Num do serve a certain very practical
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.44,0:39:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,pragmatic use youthfulness\Nand you say oh this is what it feels
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.07,0:39:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,like to feel peaceful yes and you tell\Npeople you know with a little inner
