Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that is true. Okay,\N>> but when you become sophisticated,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.92,0:40:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to recognize that that\Nprofound sense of peacefulness is even
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.88,0:40:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there is is there even when you're not\Nexperiencing it consciously. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.88,0:41:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Even when you're upset, I was upset, but\Nthat didn't really change the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.16,0:41:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that within myself there is that which\Nwas not upsettable because
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.04,0:41:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> it can't be upset cuz it's not\Nupsettable,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.52,0:41:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,>> right?\N>> You know, just like I can't upset the
