Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.07,0:42:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,uh\Nexternalism of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.48,0:42:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm.\N>> But it wouldn't really affect the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.20,0:42:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,internal peacefulness of it. The\Ninternal peacefulness cannot be
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,disturbed\Nbecause that's an expression of the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.44,0:42:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,presence of God within me as the\Nawareness of my own existence which
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.92,0:43:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't fluctuate from moment to moment.\NBut its expression would fluctuate. I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.35,0:43:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,could say well I could have answered\Nthat more eloquently
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.20,0:43:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's thinkingness.\NSo thinkingness is has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.59,0:43:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,differentiated\N>> from uh peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.92,0:43:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thinkingness is the quickest way to\Ndestroy peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.72,0:43:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes years of practice to be able to\Nindulge in thinking this and maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.56,0:43:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,peace of mind simultaneously.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.59,0:43:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the time I can do it. I can be\Naware that I'm trying to be as eloquent
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.07,0:43:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as I can be with you.\NAnd um you know I say on a superficial
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.44,0:43:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,level apprehensive that I'm not being\Nbut on an inner level it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.11,0:43:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,disturbing any peace at all because the\Nreality of my existence and my intention
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.96,0:43:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is not being altered by anything that\Ngoes on in this room or anything that's
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.59,0:44:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,being said. So is um when we have say\Ncompassion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.16,0:44:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for another person that's in you know\Nand um that's entirely different than
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.04,0:44:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,inner peace.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.96,0:44:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um compassion is is a\N>> it's not entirely different but it's a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.11,0:44:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,different\N>> it's a different example.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.64,0:44:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well yeah you're good. You're right.\NYou're right. Um so I would classify as
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.35,0:44:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,inner pieces in a whole structure\Nof itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.48,0:44:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh yeah. Okay.\N>> Um compassion is you know compassion you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.00,0:44:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,feel for another one's hurt. It's a\Ndifferent whole different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.07,0:44:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> But um that was a question someone had.\NIs inner peace the same as compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.24,0:44:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which I feel that since we've talked\Nthat it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.56,0:44:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Compassion's in a whole different\Ncategory.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.56,0:44:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can feel compassion for\Nyourself as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.20,0:45:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everybody should have compassion\Nfor themsel as a human being to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.56,0:45:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that being a human being is difficult.\N>> Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.76,0:45:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That you're deserving of uh certain love\Nand forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.35,0:45:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,out of compassion for your own existence\Nas a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.56,0:45:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember consciously asking to\Nbe
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.72,0:45:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or be born\N>> or to be a child. I don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.11,0:45:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,consciously asking any of that. That all\Noccurred of itself spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.11,0:45:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,without asking me about it.\N>> I don't remember being asked, do you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.92,0:45:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,want to do want to exist?\N>> Do you want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.35,0:45:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to experience life? I don't\Nknow. Nobody ever asked me that. So
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.35,0:45:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,through\N>> it was superimposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.28,0:45:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So through meditation we awaken the\Ninner peace but it could also be through
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.28,0:45:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplation couldn't it?\N>> Yes indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.07,0:45:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh I mean it doesn't have to be\Nmeditation. It could be
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.68,0:46:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> you know you're contemplating\Nuh a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.07,0:46:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a problem or a situation and\N>> when the answer comes you have this
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.20,0:46:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,profound knowingness that is more or\Nless an inner peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.59,0:46:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh yeah.\NIn fact, you can be at pe at at inner,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.24,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, peaceful even when you're not\Nat peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.76,0:46:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You know, you can be very accepting of\Nwhatever your state of consciousness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.64,0:46:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So overall, you're at peace with the\Nfact that you're upset. You know what
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.31,0:46:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying? The par it may sound\Nparadoxical, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.83,0:46:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we're landing in a plane and it\Nmay crash at any moment, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.28,0:46:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel fear come up at your solar\Nplexus
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.80,0:46:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,did not really affect your overall peace\Nbecause your overall peace accepted that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.92,0:46:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,fearfulness of dying is coming up\Nbecause you're about about to crash and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.83,0:47:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about to die.\NSo there was on the one hand fear, there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.96,0:47:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,was on the other hand a peace. If it\Nhappens, it happens. If it doesn't, it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.76,0:47:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't.\N>> Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.20,0:47:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And I'm just being a human being.\N>> Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.16,0:47:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,>> A normal human being would feel fear as\Nthey're about to crash. So you at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.56,0:47:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with that fearfulness was okay.\NUhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.00,0:47:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okayesseness. H.\NSo, if you had something to say to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.76,0:47:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,our people uh that are watching this um\Nabout inner peace, what would your words
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.59,0:47:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,be?\Nto accept the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.07,0:47:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the the reality of one's level of\Nconsciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.76,0:47:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times no matter what it might be.\NTo just accept whatever one's level of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.07,0:47:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness is\Naccepting then not the content of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.35,0:48:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness\Nbut consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.48,0:48:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh so experientially and by looking at\Nit I'm aware of how consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.59,0:48:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,functions,\Nhow it is, how it's experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.72,0:48:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,>> how it's perceived and I accept the\Ntotality of that. So I can be at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.31,0:48:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with upsetness because I accept that\Nupsetness is appropriate at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.48,0:48:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when we were afraid the plane\Nwas about to crash. Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.20,0:48:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um, we all accepted the fear, but nobody\Nfelt upset that they were fearful,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.64,0:48:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> right?\N>> They just accepted that, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.88,0:48:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's afraid they're about to\Ncrash.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.96,0:48:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm.\N>> Because we were
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.28,0:48:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,few moments from death. Everybody was\Nfacing a few moments from death
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.35,0:48:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> together. And there was a profound peace\Nin the plane. It was peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.20,0:48:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Quiet.\N>> Whole plane full of people were about to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.28,0:49:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,die. Everybody puts their head in their\Nlap and everybody's at peace with the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.48,0:49:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,fact that we're about to die.\N>> It was paradoxical. Wasn't that very
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.48,0:49:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting phenomena?\N>> Anybody who's looking at this has ever
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.64,0:49:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,been in that experience will know what\Nwe're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.48,0:49:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> The stewardist comes around and says,\N"Put your pillow on your lap. Put your
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.80,0:49:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,head on your pillow and stay there and\NI'll tell you when it's safe to come
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.80,0:49:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,up." And somehow some kind of strange\Npeace prevails. Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.40,0:49:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm.\NSomething in an inner knowingness or the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.92,0:49:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,inner knowingness\Nwithin consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.52,0:49:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm.\N>> Which is really an expression of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.07,0:49:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity\Nas conscious awareness without
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.96,0:49:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,articulating it or thinkingness.\NUh so peace really comes when you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.48,0:49:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,eliminate and transcend thinkingness.\NUh have no thoughts about it. So as I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.96,0:50:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,talk to you right now, I have no\Nthoughts about it. If I stop and think
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.52,0:50:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about it, then I'll create anxiety. Am I\Nsaying what I want to say? Am I doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.76,0:50:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,eloquently? Am I speaking clearly\Nenough? Is it being recorded properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.20,0:50:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I stop and start asking\Nquestions, I've I've lost the very thing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.11,0:50:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for.\NSo peace to me means accepting however
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.16,0:50:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it is right now is however it is right\Nnow. the fact that I might be more
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.72,0:50:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,eloquent. I might speak more loudly,\Nmore clearly, better articulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.48,0:50:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I accept that that's all part of the\Nreality of human existence. And I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.40,0:50:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,feel upset about it. I'm at peace with\Nthe fact that I'm uh that peacefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.28,0:50:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a 100% all the time\Nuh prevailing dominant state of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.59,0:50:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.\NIt is and it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.96,0:50:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I accept it eliminates it\Nas real anxiety. So I can be at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.31,0:51:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with the fact that I feel anxiety. How's\Nthat grab you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.11,0:51:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a winner, baby. Hey, I can be at\Npeace with the fact that I'm not at
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.76,0:51:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,peace at all. There you go. Of course\Nyou're upset, baby. Why not? You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.48,0:51:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you could stumble and make a fool of\Nyourself and sound like an idiot. Uh, so
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.16,0:51:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept that.\NAnd that's fine with me. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.44,0:51:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> Everybody, anybody who's ever spoken in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.00,0:51:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,public knows what I we're talking about.\N>> Yeah. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.00,0:51:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, thank you. Thank you so much for\Nyour thoughts on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.92,0:51:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you for asking me.
